The,Open,Fraud,Detection,Project,OFDEP,is,a,fraud,detection,API,that,is,designed,to,detect,suspicious,users,early,on,preventing,activities,like,fraudulent,purchases,invalid,account,creations,and,comment,spam,Security,devices,can,query,OFDEP,to,determine,the,odds,that,a,given,user,or,transaction,is,bad,The,API,is,currently,in,beta,and,supports,IP,email,address,and,username,look,ups,It,returns,results,in,XML,but,JSON,will,also,be,supported,in,the,near,future